{"tid":2318183,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"請連仔設計新連登動物-連魚！","createTime":"2020-12-09T06:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T17:03:12.000Z","uid":225828,"like":11,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e561090e4d25df1ef0ec4a56ed8843ae15ee36f6","tid":2318183,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:57:25.000Z","msg":"請會員<span class=\"gold\">#1連尼住，#3望遠</span>，或者其他有心嘅巴絲打，設計連魚🐟<br />\n<br />\n連魚emoji諗咗幾個：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.好似每隻連登動物都有嘅連登emoji咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望連魚嘅版本係：<br />\n<br />\n中間有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺度拍手，然後連魚🐟就鯉躍龍門咁不停跳過拍緊手嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.連魚喺度blu blu blu咁嘔泡泡🐟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.連魚好似街市擺檔啲魚咁樣不停咁跳下跳下反下反下，隱藏combo可以係<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> + 不停跳下反下嘅連魚<br />\n= <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抓住跳下反下嘅連魚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.連魚剩返排魚骨喺度喊，類似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />+<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />混合體<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.連魚喺個金魚缸裏面不停咁轉圈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.兩條連魚喺度接吻，周圍有啲心心咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7.條連魚係雞泡魚，不停咁突啲刺出嚟又收返埋啲刺🐡"},{"pid":"a23fd73b927000a28542a5141f4bf80af6f3d994","tid":2318183,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"請有心人設計連魚，謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1d6c4ddaab3fd9f0ebafb8c1f44df66da25293","tid":2318183,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"點解係魚"},{"p